* For implementing profiling, load the package profilercc in the modulo you want to profile and
  annotate predicates with the directive ":- cost_center pred/arity". In the Ciao top leve, load
  module "library(profilercc/profiler_utils)", then use the goal "profile_reset, prodile(Goal), profile_sump."

* Analyze file by hand
  use_module(library(profilercc/profiler_utils)).
  set_pp_flag(mgu_sh_optimize,optimal).
  set_pp_flag(modes,as_sharing).
  set_pp_flag(types,none).
  set_pp_flag(collapse_ai_vers,off).
  set_pp_flag(pp_info, on).
  module('experiments/sharing_experiments.pl').
  profile(analyze(as_sharing)).
  profile_dump.
